summary: Last week’s Stylist had an interview w/Jodie Comer (I’m loving her in Killing Eve + so pleased to hear there’s going to be a 2nd...
body:
Last week’s Stylist had an interview w/Jodie Comer (I’m loving her in Killing Eve + so pleased to hear there’s going to be a 2nd series).  The week before they had a really good piece on women + their relationship w/food + eating plus a bit on Fanny Eaton (Pre-Raphaelite muse). 

Saw the last episode of The Cry - overall I liked it esp the twist of what actually happened to the missing baby.
